This script is a set of building blocks, that will be used in Game to generated Advertisement, as one might see it at an airport or late-night tv.
The pronounciation: Professional Media advertisement that is still audible when played in repeat loop over traffic. Everything in this add will be tailored to short attention spans. Similar to advertising a new avengers movie on the radio.


